graph LR
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>v1.21.0-18]

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|authentication| OpenShiftOAuth[OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>OAuth 2.0]
    Dashboard -->|resource mgmt| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP]
    Dashboard -->|metrics query| Prometheus[Prometheus/Thanos<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS]
    Dashboard -->|TLS certs| ServiceCert[Service Certificate Controller<br/>service-cert]
    Dashboard -->|routing| OpenShiftRouter[OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP edge TLS]

    %% Runtime Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|runtime| NodeJS[Node.js 20.x<br/>Required]
    Dashboard -->|K8s client| K8sClientNode["@kubernetes/client-node<br/>0.12.2"]
    Dashboard -->|web framework| Fastify[Fastify 4.28.1<br/>Backend]
    Dashboard -->|UI framework| React[React 18.2.0<br/>Frontend]
    Dashboard -->|UI components| PatternFly[PatternFly 6.3.1<br/>Component Library]
    Dashboard -->|state mgmt| Redux[Redux 4.2.0<br/>State Management]
    Dashboard -->|routing| ReactRouter[React Router 7.6.2<br/>Frontend Routing]
    Dashboard -->|bundling| Webpack[Webpack 5.96.1<br/>Build Tooling]

    %% Internal ODH Component Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|read CRs| ODHOperator[opendatahub-operator<br/>DataScienceCluster, DSCInit]
    Dashboard -->|create/manage| Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks<br/>Notebook CRs]
    Dashboard -->|read status| KServe[KServe<br/>InferenceService]
    Dashboard -->|create/manage| ModelRegistry[Model Registry Operator<br/>ModelRegistry CRs]
    Dashboard -->|integrates| ODHModelController[odh-model-controller<br/>Serving Runtimes]
    Dashboard -->|manages| Workbenches[Workbenches<br/>Notebook Instances]
    Dashboard -->|integrates| Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Pipeline Runs]
    Dashboard -->|displays| TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service<br/>Bias Metrics]
    Dashboard -->|manages| Kueue[Kueue<br/>Workload Queues]
    Dashboard -->|manages| CodeFlare[CodeFlare Operator<br/>Distributed Training]
    Dashboard -.->|optional| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh - Istio<br/>Traffic Routing, mTLS]

    %% Console Integration
    Dashboard -->|registers links| OpenShiftConsole[OpenShift Console<br/>Navigation Integration]

    %% External Services (Optional)
    Dashboard -.->|telemetry| Segment[Segment Analytics<br/>Optional, 443/TCP]
    Dashboard -.->|documentation| ExternalDocs[External Documentation URLs<br/>HTTPS/443]

    %% Model Registry to Storage
    ModelRegistry -->|storage| S3[S3 Storage<br/>Model Artifacts]

    %% Dynamic Plugins (Module Federation)
    subgraph Plugins["Dynamic Plugins (Module Federation)"]
        GenAI[Gen AI Plugin<br/>LLM Management]
        ModelRegPlugin[Model Registry Plugin<br/>Versioning UI]
        FeatureStore[Feature Store Plugin<br/>Feature Engineering]
        LMEval[LM Eval Plugin<br/>Benchmarking]
        KServePlugin[KServe Plugin<br/>Model Serving UI]
        ModelServing[Model Serving Plugin<br/>Deployment UI]
        ModelTraining[Model Training Plugin<br/>Training Jobs]
    end

    Dashboard -.->|dynamic load| GenAI
    Dashboard -.->|dynamic load| ModelRegPlugin
    Dashboard -.->|dynamic load| FeatureStore
    Dashboard -.->|dynamic load| LMEval
    Dashboard -.->|dynamic load| KServePlugin
    Dashboard -.->|dynamic load| ModelServing
    Dashboard -.->|dynamic load| ModelTraining

